        <div class="fs-2 text-center mb-3">
          Event Tools
        </div>
        <p>Putting together event packs, planning encounters, statting your monsters, it can all become a formatting nightmare</p>
        <p>We've crunched the numbers, and planned the document.</p>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-placement="top" data-bs-trigger="hover" data-bs-content="We make it possible to create and timetable your encounters, as well as generate that into an easily readable document.">Encounter timetabling <small class="text-danger">Coming Soon!</small></li>
