          <li class="list-group-item" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-placement="top" data-bs-trigger="hover" data-bs-content="Do you need an event pack telling your players what to expect? Maybe they need directions or gate codes to your venue? We've taken care of it, and will even send it to your players">Event Pack PDF generation and automatic e-mailing</li>
