        </ul>
      </div>
  <div id="downsides" class="col text-center px-5">
    <div class="fs-2 text-center mb-3">
      Whats The Catch?
    </div>
    <p>Life has taught us all that there is no such thing as a free meal, so of course you want to know what the downsides are.</p>
    <p>There are a few, see what you think</p>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
      <li class="list-group-item" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-placement="top" data-bs-trigger="hover" data-bs-content="Whilst we would love to keep this free, there is a small cost to running the website. We do not aim to make a profit and are always reviewing this price">Booking events with us has a one off <%= currencyOutput(config.hostingCharge) %> fee per event</li>
      <li class="list-group-item" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-placement="top" data-bs-trigger="hover" data-bs-content="Securely taking payments requires a payment provider. We are looking to include others, but for now PayPal is the most widespread and accessible">Payments are processed by PayPal, some love it, some hate it</li>
      <li class="list-group-item" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-placement="top" data-bs-trigger="hover" data-bs-content="This is both a pro and a con. We hope that growing the community is a boon to every one">A shared platform means more visibility, and more competition</li>
